(118, 0, '<p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp;任何一个当地人提到巴拿山，便会兴奋和滔滔不绝起来，只因那里是芒果的避暑胜地，巴拿山距芒果市以西约四十公里，海拨1487米，山上的平均气温比山下低8摄氏度左右，凉爽的感觉对身处热带的芒果人来说相当诱人。<br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af70b09c671.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af70f7e4e1c.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 26px; background-color: white;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;巴拿山登山缆车是世界吉尼斯单线最长、落差最大记录的保持者，由法国人投资建设，全程约5000米。<br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71276acfc.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af712716e36.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1901年法国殖民者首先发现了这片乐土，他们把这里作为将军和家眷们的度假胜地。第一次世界大战期间，法国士兵和家属无法回国，便大规模的修建各类建筑。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71710f424.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71700f424.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;登上巴拿山，可以一览芒果的全城风貌，体验云端看海的景观，站在山顶眺望，心情异常开阔。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71a4632ea.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71a37de29.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;位于山上城堡建筑，基本上呈现法式造型，色彩斑斓，犹如一个童话世界，地下拥有东南亚最大的机动设施游乐场。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71caca2dd.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71ca7a120.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;至今在巴拿山的半山留有一百年多年前的酒窖，对于红酒颇有研究的人们大可亲身去探访一下真正的法国酒窖，在酒窖外的露台同样可以一览巴拿山旖旎的风光。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71edb71b0.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af71ed40d99.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;浓郁的法式建筑风格，仿佛置身于欧洲小镇，体味这渗入骨子里的法式浪漫。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af72154c4b4.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af72151e848.jpg"/></p>', '', 0, '发岘之旅', ''),
(119, 0, '<p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; background-color: white;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 32px; background-color: white;"> 越南海洋有很多岛屿，其中有往昔曾处于东海“丝绸之路”上的占婆岛，被联合国教科文组织UNESCO承认为“世界生物圈储备区”,也是国内外游客参观、潜水、观赏珊瑚的理想地址。</span><br/></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background: white;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2a16039387.jpg"/></p><fieldset style="border: 0px; margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 0px 2px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 1; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; min-width: 1.8em; min-height: 1.6em; border-top-left-radius: 80%; border-top-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-right-radius: 90%; border-bottom-left-radius: 20%; line-height: 1; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box;">1</section></section><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box;">占婆岛两宝</section></strong></span></section></fieldset><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 燕子洞和活体珊瑚有着占婆岛两宝之称，蜾蠃洞和枯洞是燕子在悬崖筑巢的地方。燕窝作为占婆岛特产，每年仅开采一周。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2a18a76417.jpg" style=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2a18990f56.jpg" style=""/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧绿的海水清澈可见，如果海浪平静、阳光明媚，游客可乘坐玻璃底船观赏水下舞动的珊瑚，喜欢探索的游客亦可选择潜水，亲眼观赏奇妙的珊瑚、海参和五颜六色鱼类。每年7月至9月的能见度达15至30米，是潜水的最佳时间。</span></p><fieldset style="border: 0px; margin: 0.8em 0px 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 0px 2px 2px; box-sizing: border-box; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; line-height: 1; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.4em; min-width: 1.8em; min-height: 1.6em; border-top-left-radius: 80%; border-top-right-radius: 100%; border-bottom-right-radius: 90%; border-bottom-left-radius: 20%; line-height: 1; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box;">2</section></section><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: 0.4em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box;">簸箕船</section></strong></span></section></fieldset><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">说到出海就不得不说越南中部渔民特有的小船——簸箕船，就是用竹子编制成圆形大竹篓状的小船，外表涂上了一层柏油，用来放水。这里海岸较浅，较大的渔船无法靠岸，渔民就划着这种圆形的簸箕小船，把大船上的渔产卸下来，运回岸上。随着游客增多，簸箕船已成为越南中部海边特有的一道风景。</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background: white;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2a23d57bcf.jpg"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '', ''),
(143, 0, '<p style="line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;奥黛(AoDai)，是越南的国服。“ao”源于汉语“袄”，在现代越语里“ao”则指遮盖颈部以下的服饰，而“dai”的意思是“长”。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a36153bebc2.jpg" width="300" height="400" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 300px; height: 400px;"/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 奥黛通常使用丝绸等软性布料，上衣是一件长衫，类似中国旗袍，胸袖剪裁非常合身，突显女性玲珑有致的曲线，而两侧开高叉至腰部，走路时前后两片裙摆随风飘逸，下半身配上一条喇叭筒的长裤，因此日常生活的行、住、坐、卧都很方便。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a362189c671.jpg" width="300" height="476" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 300px; height: 476px;"/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em; background: white;"><span style=";font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333">　 大家常常看到越南街头骑自行车和摩托车的奥黛少女，在惊羡其飘逸时，也常常为她们捏把汗，担心裙带绞进车里不安全，其实这种担心是多余的。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a36258cdfe6.jpg" width="350" height="246" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 350px; height: 246px;"/></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;满街婀娜飘逸的奥黛，就像中国的旗袍、日本的和服以及印度的纱丽一样出名。奥黛发展的初期受到了中国影响，后来又融合了欧美文化，所以说奥黛是越南的旗袍并不准确。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a3626fc28cb.jpg" width="323" height="340" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 323px; height: 340px;"/></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;现在，越南政府鼓励人们在正式场合穿着奥黛，并成为女性公务人员、旅馆接待、新闻主播、航空公司空姐以及高中女生的标准制服。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a3628622551.jpg" width="280" height="412" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 280px; height: 412px;"/></p>', '', 0, '发岘美女', ''),
(144, 0, '<p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;近日，一组越南空姐在飞机中身着比基尼的照片在网络热传。从照片中看来空姐们个个笑容甜美、身材火辣，有网友调侃称“为了美丽的空姐也要去旅游”。不过涉及的越南航空公司却予以否认，称并非官方发布的照片。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 据介绍，身着比基尼的越南空姐并非真正的空姐，只是当地的模特。现在就来看看网络热传的越南空姐火辣照吧。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a3639b0f424.jpg" style="width: 325px; height: 244px;" width="325" height="244" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a3639a66ff3.jpg" style="width: 294px; height: 200px;" width="294" height="200" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a363996ea05.jpg" style="width: 350px; height: 198px;" width="350" height="198" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a36398487ab.jpg" style="width: 365px; height: 219px;" width="365" height="219" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 对于爱美的小伙伴来说，美女也是另一种不同的风景，我们可以为美食去旅游，为美景去旅游，为美女当然也是可以的啦！</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '发岘美女', ''),
(145, 0, '<p><span id="_baidu_bookmark_start_5" style="display: none; line-height: 0px;">‍</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">我们常常在说到海滨度假城市时，绝对会脱口而出的就有“阳光，沙滩，比基尼”。而异域风情的芒果拥有着一片热情的、绵延30公里的沙滩海岸<span style="font-family: 宋体;">，<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">雪白的细沙、摇曳的椰子树，海天相接，一幅宽阔的天然画卷，背景是清透的海的蓝、天之蓝，云朵是惟一流动着的油彩——这处沙滩在2005年被联合国教科文组织评为“世界六大美丽沙滩”之一。</span></span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">芒果的海滩是干净的白沙滩，沙质细腻无杂质，赤脚走在上面不用担心被尖锐物体扎伤。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 假日的午后，静静地躺在海滩上，海上的阳光一直都是那样地温暖惬意，听着海浪一波一波地拍打着岸边的声音。就这样完全放松身心感受着芒果每一个自然细胞的活力。整个下午就这样度过也不会觉得寂寞，只有从内到外的平和。如果能和爱人一起享受这样的午后，那是再好不过的了。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a364c9e8b25.jpg" style="width: 480px; height: 320px;" width="480" height="320" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a364c8c28cb.jpg" style="width: 483px; height: 320px;" width="483" height="320" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-indent: 21px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;漫步在芒果海滩，你会发现有很多高鼻子蓝眼睛的欧美人。因为芒果舒适的气候，和宁静的</span><a href="http://travel.sina.com.cn/" target="_blank" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: black; text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; color: black;">旅行</span></a><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">环境，让很多欧美人爱上了这里，他们每次一来都住上半个月，甚至一个月之久。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a364ffbebc2.jpg" style="width: 427px; height: 240px;" width="427" height="240" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a364fc5b8d8.jpg" style="width: 360px; height: 240px;" width="360" height="240" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">当我们说到比基尼，就会说到穿着比基尼的美女。越南的小蛮腰是出了名的美，而当她们由奥黛换上性感的比基尼，怕是人人见了都无法移开目光。还有来自不同国家的游客，在海滩上尽情地舒展她们比基尼的魅力，到处都是移动着的风景线。阳光下的沙滩，沙滩上的比基尼，这一切都在芒果海滩快乐绽放。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a36522d1cef.jpg" style="width: 372px; height: 280px;" width="372" height="280" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a36522a037a.jpg" style="width: 358px; height: 240px;" width="358" height="240" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title=""/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;</span><span id="_baidu_bookmark_end_6" style="display: none; line-height: 0px;">‍</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '发岘美女', ''),
