ieldset><fieldset style="width: 100%; border: none; margin: 0.5em 0px; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; background-color: rgb(248, 247, 245); box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) -1px 1px 2px; box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section style="border-width: 20px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(153, 153, 153) rgb(153, 153, 153); box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section style="margin-top: -38px; margin-left: 1px; border-width: 18px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(255, 255, 240) rgb(255, 255, 240); box-sizing: border-box;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><br/></section></section></section></fieldset><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '海云湾', ''),
(116, 0, '<fieldset style="border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: justify; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;" class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 0px;">﻿</span>芒果皇冠假日酒店 (Crowne PlazaDanang) 位于世界著名的芒果海滩，这是美国福布斯杂志读者投票评出的全球六大最奢华海滩之一，临近联合国教科文住址评出的四大世界遗产（顺化旧皇城、会安古镇、耶稣圣地和丰芽格邦国家公园）。酒店总面积达20万平方米，彰显高档气派之风，采用经典的西式设计，但恰到好处地融入亚洲特色风格。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af7587d1cef.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af75a91ab3f.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af75a75b8d8.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af75a6d9701.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 35px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">一出酒店，立刻进入一片私人海滩CHINABEACH，人少，私密度高，蓝天碧海白沙滩，白滑细嫩。酒店拥有535间豪华客 房和套房，一侧俯瞰碧蓝的大海，另一侧则是繁华的芒果市景色。酒店大堂、功能室、餐厅、酒吧和服务区占据了2-3层的宽敞空间，周围环绕着超大游泳池和绿 树葱笼的热带花园。皇冠假日酒店的特色不在于赌场，而是酒店建造在沙滩之上（这是芒果唯一建在沙滩上的酒店），它的泳池靠近海边，景色非常美丽。泳池旁边有吧台，一边游，一边喝，非常惬意。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af75e531975.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af75e4cdfe6.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">前台服务的人员都基本会中文、英文，叫车、换钱、引导都不是问题，如果和司机沟通不了还可以记下前台电话，有需要时，打去和前台交代事情，再让前台转述给对方听，例如司机，非常方便。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">酒店距离芒果机场7公里，15分钟车程，距离市区3公里，车程8分钟，交通极为便利。酒店拥有豪华宽敞舒适的客房，能在房间内观赏美丽的海景以及芒果美丽的市景。酒店有全日西餐厅，中餐厅，游泳池，健身中心， 桑拿，KTV，娱乐城，以及各类水上运动服务。</span></p><br/></section></fieldset><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '发岘之旅', ''),
(117, 0, '<p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 20px;">越南广南省会安古街晚上7点，机动车禁止通行，五颜六色的灯笼打造了一个奇幻、舒适的空间。不知何时起，灯笼成为了古街夜间文化的像征</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px;">。</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2976b8d24d.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp;在会安，从会馆、公共场所到街道,民居灯笼随处可见,给游客一种既熟悉又陌生的感觉.在怀河岸上欣赏绚丽多彩的灯笼街,游客将更加了解为何会安能够连续被环球网网上评选的2013年十大旅游城市榜排第二。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a297e51e848.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; 会安古城内到处都挂着五彩的美丽灯笼, 会安现在是越南最大的灯笼制作中心，城内的很多家庭都以制作灯笼为生，世界各地的旅游者来到会安，也都会选购一两款漂亮的灯笼带回家留作纪念。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a2984303d09.jpg" width="372" height="280" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 372px; height: 280px;"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; 会安的灯笼是多姿多彩的,有圆型的,有椭圆型的,还有帽子型的等等, 会安的灯笼不似国内大红灯笼高高挂的豪放气派，却有着精致的考究和巧妙的构思。在很多灯笼上面写着“福禄寿”，“大吉大利”等漂亮的汉字。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54a298ac66ff3.jpg" width="302" height="450" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" title="" style="width: 302px; height: 450px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp; 当夜幕降临,各种小巧玲珑,制作精巧的灯笼在宅院中和临街的建筑中次第亮起,会安就变成了一个五彩缤纷的灯笼海洋. 红色的,绿色的,蓝色的灯笼配上古城黄色的建筑,使古城的夜色变得更加迷离梦幻。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af7412ec82e.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">据说每到农历的正月十五和八月十五,是会安的“怀旧日”, 全城将统一停电,家家户户的门前挂起五彩灯笼.人人都会穿上古装, 满城的五彩灯笼和一轮皓月交相辉映.就像一幅意境悠远的古画。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; text-align: center;">晚上在街道上漫无目标的行走, 仔细品味那些优美可爱的灯笼，看亭台楼阁上都挂满了灯笼,连很多餐馆里的灯都制作成了灯笼的形状,街上的行人行走缓慢,怡然自得,看见手拿相机的我，都会满面笑容的点头示意。</span></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af742ea037a.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af742e3d090.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 除了传统的灯笼，这里也不乏现代创新元素的融入，不时有两三个婀娜多姿，身穿白色奥黛的越南女子从街上飘然走过. 仿佛是在电影中看到的场景。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af744b1ab3f.png"/></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; 最后来到香江边上.恍然来到了江南水乡.江边建筑上的灯光倒映在江中.水面上波光粼粼，流光溢彩，不时有一两艘船在暗夜里缓缓驶过，只听见轻轻的浆声和流水声。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '', 0, '发岘之旅', ''),
(102, 0, '<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;很多人喜欢一句诗：面朝大海，春暖花开,这便是山茶半岛的真实写照。打开车窗，海风破有些清爽，通向山茶半岛的纵深依赖一条狭长的海岸公路。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3UwppdG7LJMicogmcaZOseiag/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3UwppdG7LJMicogmcaZOseiag/0" data-ratio="0.6640316205533597" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c39HqscZ8vUkT6a7qiahF3ApA/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c39HqscZ8vUkT6a7qiahF3ApA/0" data-ratio="0.5079051383399209" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 山茶半岛某一个角度的大海呈现一个半圆型的海湾，极其巨大到让人惊诧这鬼斧神工，有点像那月牙儿，又如浑圆的玉盆。站在这片海之前，我顿时被这无边的浩瀚与完美的澈蓝所震撼。这是芒果最正气的一面，将海、天、山、云揉作最壮美的画卷，这里拥有几乎等于东南亚之最的海之纯净。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3mX5TOQ6UbE2lFCypIAmBSw/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3mX5TOQ6UbE2lFCypIAmBSw/0" data-ratio="0.6976284584980237" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; <span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; 山茶半岛层峦叠嶂、森林茂密，保持原生态的原始森林里出没着珍惜的爪哇猴、长尾猴、红脸鸡。在驻足山茶半岛的任何一条环岸公路上，不难看到凭栏上的猴型雕塑，有点像印度的哈努曼。望向天，天蓝得不像话，望向海，海依然蓝得没话说，望向花，却有一丝缕的暗香飘进鼻子。</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3rutLJ9NX72eJiclZzo1PMlw/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3rutLJ9NX72eJiclZzo1PMlw/0" data-ratio="1.4217171717171717" data-w="396"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3Xz5Q88hOIySSI0GgpFe2kw/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3Xz5Q88hOIySSI0GgpFe2kw/0" data-ratio="0.6280623608017817" data-w="449"/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3ofNAGXkuVY28BykGibAFhlQ/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3ofNAGXkuVY28BykGibAFhlQ/0" data-ratio="0.6996047430830039" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12pt;">山茶半岛上坐落着高达</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">69</span>米<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12pt;">的亚洲最大观音雕像，这是山茶半岛的标志性建筑，整个观音像纯白而洁美，让人忍不住一再驻足流连，并且往返。据说芒果有三座灵应寺，山茶半岛便拥有其一，灵应寺附近的绿树、翘檐、蓝天构成了一幅和谐曼丽的画面。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3icicx9hNAyzxic7ayu3kT0c4g/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3icicx9hNAyzxic7ayu3kT0c4g/0" data-ratio="0.466403162055336" data-w=""/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c30icoiaiahFAujAo5OaV2kzJxg/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c30icoiaiahFAujAo5OaV2kzJxg/0" data-ratio="0.6620553359683794" data-w=""/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c38HMGIh8r54cv6fJfyPibibjg/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c38HMGIh8r54cv6fJfyPibibjg/0" data-ratio="1.33201581027668" data-w=""/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;山茶半岛还拥有据说可以颠覆整个东南亚酒店格局的芒果洲际酒店。为凸显渔村风情，洲际酒店</span>特别以传统的筲箕船，改造成斜拉式的升降机，以连接建于山坡上的酒店大堂和山坡下近 200 间的别墅套房、沙滩、泳池及餐厅等设施。虽然乘搭时间只有短短 1 分钟，但已足够让大家透过观景玻璃窗欣赏到广阔的南海景致，甚至有种乘坐着筲箕船出海的感觉。</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c32CnEDjookoYm4NaaS7a4AQ/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c32CnEDjookoYm4NaaS7a4AQ/0" data-ratio="0.6620553359683794" data-w=""/></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; letter-spacing: 1px;"> 位于酒店大堂旁，坐拥全酒店最美景致的餐厅，亦是酒店内的亮点。餐厅布置大玩花巧设计元素，每个部分都有不同风格，未食先为大家带来无限惊喜。当中采用传统越南斗笠 Non-la 设计的无敌海景用餐区最瞩目，而自助美食区，则用了巨型鱼网作为布置，花尽心思的创意，处处不遗「渔」力。</span><br style="TEXT-ALIGN: left"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c30HVnMBDmGlPRxRHLnQAXgQ/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c30HVnMBDmGlPRxRHLnQAXgQ/0" data-ratio="0.66600790513834" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3WzNdF9xqHMTZo0GPZjIDmQ/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFjsceBVoVZlSKBYBnuuwp9c3WzNdF9xqHMTZo0GPZjIDmQ/0" data-ratio="0.6620553359683794" data-w=""/></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong>山茶半岛-猴子道婚纱照</strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%;">芒果山茶半岛的无敌海景、壮美翠山、浩瀚蓝天，乃至那山、那花都足以在一生中烙下再次重逢的期待。这一片美景只属于懂她的人，在山茶半岛的徜徉间，我已情迷。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 12pt; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 山茶半岛从来给人奇幻色彩的印象，对于笔者，更加有彷如世外桃源的感觉。踏上半岛，车子驶在狭长的岸线，情迷之处由此带起。一条公路缠腰山腰，一路延伸，心中便生出一股不断前进和穿越的欲望，真的想看看路的尽头是什么，但却从不知。公路上的景观是一望无际的大海，海中浮着几艘小渔船，还隐约可以看到海洋蓝色的不同深浅演绎！眼前极目是南中国海的景致，背面则是山景与植物所包围，人烟稀落，让身心都不期然进入宁静的待机模式吧!</span></span></p><p style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px;"></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; max-width: 100%; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px;"> 沿着山路深入，车子驶到只能一辆车身行驶的蜿蜒小路上，两边被原生树木包围着，而后视野又重新开阔，便是到达隐秘圣地——千年许愿树。许愿树气根错落，深入扎根泥土，枝繁叶茂。有时，会有三两情侣到树下参拜。可能现代通讯科技发达，曾经的隐世之地也越发多人前来取景拍摄婚纱照，取其树形美态和神圣之意。</span></span></span></p><p style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: normal; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WHITE-SPACE: pre-wrap; MIN-HEIGHT: 1em; MARGIN-TOP: 0px"><br style="TEXT-ALIGN: left"/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09zVztmxdf8UYjqbicRzjCSeuA/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09zVztmxdf8UYjqbicRzjCSeuA/0" data-ratio="0.308300395256917" data-w=""/></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09zcPp6322PhNibkzvicrFm5dQA/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09zcPp6322PhNibkzvicrFm5dQA/0" data-ratio="1.4938574938574938" data-w="407"/></p><p style="word-wrap: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: left; min-height: 1em; margin-top: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;最爱是黄昏之前时候到访，回程时候夕阳的金光散到海面闪耀生辉，仿佛是对你前来山茶半岛探访的回礼。此时正是希望找个地方静等落霞，饱眼福之余更要果腹的好时光。我们一边路经山林景观，好容易忽略隐蔽在其中的一家餐厅,名叫Bay Ban。这间别有洞天的餐馆，从门口沿小路下去到达沙滩，确实一个赏景美食地。</span></p><p style="word-wrap: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 1em; margin-top: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 32px; text-indent: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; TEXT-ALIGN: left"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img style="BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; HEIGHT: auto !important; WIDTH: auto !important; VISIBILITY: visible !important" src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09z5ozUntNwhSoPlyrRcibMMag/0" data-src="http://mmsns.qpic.cn/mmsns/0bbjeeIGFju7ictF4qicNEow8xo5s2B09z5ozUntNwhSoPlyrRcibMMag/0" data-ratio="0.6620553359683794" data-w=""/></p><p style="text-align: 