(101, 0, '<p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 芒果是著名的海鲜产地，各类野生生猛海鲜无所不有。种类繁多的贝类海鲜，用最地道的越式炮制，让你吃到爽！</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;"><strong style="font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: center; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 240);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 4px 10px; border-top-left-radius: 2em 0.5em; border-top-right-radius: 1em 3em; border-bottom-left-radius: 1em 3em; border-bottom-right-radius: 4em 0.5em; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 4px 4px 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">海胆</span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; line-height: 1.75em;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;最新鲜的吃法是刚刚从海上捞上来就开来生吃。海胆食用的最好时候是内里的肉为金黄色，当然烤熟了也可以很美味，可以将海胆剪开一个口子，加少许柠檬汁和盐，海胆的油分和连同一起进烤箱的洋葱和香叶发挥作用，让海胆变得更鲜美可口。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://ag.amango.net/Public/static/ueditor/php/../../../../Uploads/Picture/54af78402dc6c.png"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; c